channel.title: New Development- Deven
channel.description:
Okay everyone so i quit for about 3 months after being told that i sucked and i should stop. I regained confidence and im going to make a serious effort to make a decent server. Im looking for a server to use preferably a delta to learn from. I want it to have the basics and maybe a bit more but to have room for improvement. So please suggest a source for me to use. You can also apply below to join my new team.
All i ask is for you to not flame or criticize me for trying. If you have nothing good to say dont touch the dam keyboard.
